column5: I bought these natural motion lure snakes off the internet. The video's looked promising and i have yet to use them. Anyone else by these things? Just wondering if they are any good or will be another "banjo minnow"  Mac
Search snakes they have been talked about here!
Dude, Banjo minnows ruled! Don't knock 'em!
If my memory serves me right there was a guy in here using them and he got some large mouths on them. I think he did quite well.
Hey Rich, I have seen a few of your vids  Have you ever done one of a Banjo minnow day?  forrest
Which site you buy them from?
Hey i had the bajo minnow aswell..... but caught half the amount of fish as i did with a regular powerbait worm.
